<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Account Credentials</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }
    .credentials {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Mourya Urja Matrimonial</h1>
    <p>Dear User,</p>
    <p>Thank you for registering with us. Below are your account credentials:</p>
    <div class="credentials">
      <p>Email: <span class="highlight"><%= email %></span></p>
      <p>Password: <span class="highlight"><%= password %></span></p>
    </div>
    <p>We recommend remember your password after logging in for security purposes.</p>
    <p>If you didn't register for an account, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Mourya Urja Matrimonial. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
